music/ghost-announce-2025-world-tour-with-shows-in-the-uk-europe-us-and-north-america-buy-tickets-3807064">今年春天晚些时候进行2025年世界巡回演出</a>。<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ghost-are-teasing-new-frontman-papa-v-perpetua-3835158">在此处</a>查看完整的日期列表，然后<a href="https://www.ticketmaster.co.uk/search?q=Ghost" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>访问以购买门票。</p><p> Post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ghost-tease-new-frontman-papa-v-perpetua-with-las-vegas-billboard-v-is-coming-3842804">Ghost挑逗“新”主唱Papa v Perpetua和Las Vegas Billboard：“ V Im Come”</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
